docblock.long-description:
SQL: `CALL project_list();`
ARRAY OF ARRAY: - P_ID id - P_NAME p_name - C_NAME c_name - GA_NAME ga_name - H_SERIAL h_serial - H_ID h_id

ARRAY OF ARRAY: - WO_ID - WO_NAME

ARRAY OF ARRAY: - T_SUB_TASK.* - T_GENERIC_SUB_TASK.* - T_MANUAL.*

ARRAY OF ARRAY: - GST_ID - GST_ID_M - GST_NUMBER - GST_DESCRIPTION

ARRAY OF ARRAY: - T_SUB_TASK.* - T_GENERIC_SUB_TASK.* - T_WORK_ORDER.* - T_PROJECT.*

docblock.long-description:
SQL: `SELECT * FROM T_USER WHERE U_ID=:id;`
ARRAY: - U_ID - U_NAME - U_PASSWORD - U_STATUS - U_CODE

docblock.description: get info from database about all users
docblock.long-description:
SQL: `SELECT U_ID, U_NAME, U_CODE FROM T_USER;`
ARRAY OF ARRAY - U_ID - U_NAME - U_CODE

docblock.description: get info from database about all manuals for an aircraft
docblock.long-description:
SQL: `SELECT M_ID, M_NAME, GA_NAME FROM T_MANUAL INNER JOIN T_GENERIC_AIRCRAFT ON M_ID_GA=GA_ID WHERE M_ID_GA=:id ORDER BY M_NAME;`
ARRAY OF ARRAY: - M_ID - M_NAME - GA_NAME

docblock.description: get info from database about an engine
docblock.long-description:
SQL: `SELECT * FROM T_ENGINE INNER JOIN T_GENERIC_AIRCRAFT ON E_ID_GA=GA_ID WHERE E_ID=:id`
ARRAY: - E_ID - E_ID_GA - E_ID_LOG_BOOK - E_SERIAL - E_NAME - E_TYPE - E_TIME - E_NG_CYCLE - E_NF_CYCLE

Used for ERV

ARRAY OF ARRAY: - GP_ID - GP_NUMBER - GP_NAME - GP_TYPE - GP_LOCATION - GP_DESCRIPTION

docblock.long-description:

ARRAY OF ARRAY: - GP_ID

docblock.description: get info from database about all stock parts
docblock.long-description:
SQL: `CALL stock_list();`
ARRAY OF ARRAY: - T_STOCK.* - T_GENERIC_PART.* - T_FILE po.F_ID AS PO_ID - T_FILE po.F_DIRECTORY AS PO_DIRECTORY - T_FILE po.F_NAME AS PO_NAME - T_FILE po.F_FORMAT AS PO_FORMAT - T_FILE arc.F_ID AS ARC_ID - T_FILE arc.F_DIRECTORY AS ARC_DIRECTORY - T_FILE arc.F_NAME AS ARC_NAME - T_FILE arc.F_FORMAT AS ARC_FORMAT - SUM(COALESCE(LPS_QUANTITY_NUMBER,0)) AS S_QUANTITY_USED

docblock.description: get info from database about all available stock parts
docblock.long-description:

ARRAY OF ARRAY: - T_STOCK.* - T_GENERIC_PART.* - T_FILE po.F_ID AS PO_ID - T_FILE po.F_DIRECTORY AS PO_DIRECTORY - T_FILE po.F_NAME AS PO_NAME - T_FILE po.F_FORMAT AS PO_FORMAT - T_FILE arc.F_ID AS ARC_ID - T_FILE arc.F_DIRECTORY AS ARC_DIRECTORY - T_FILE arc.F_NAME AS ARC_NAME - T_FILE arc.F_FORMAT AS ARC_FORMAT - S_QUANTITY_NUMBER - SUM(COALESCE(LPS_QUANTITY_NUMBER,0)) AS S_QUANTITY_AVAILABLE

docblock.long-description:
SQL: `CALL available_stock_list_by_po_from_gp_id(:id);`
ARRAY OF ARRAY: - T_STOCK.* - SUM(COALESCE(LPS_QUANTITY_NUMBER,0)) AS S_QUANTITY_USED - S_QUANTITY_NUMBER - SUM(COALESCE(LPS_QUANTITY_NUMBER,0)) AS S_QUANTITY_AVAILABLE

docblock.description: get info from database about all used stock parts by po for pp
